2:00:18.763 --> 2:00:20.903
Surround yourself with people
that love you for you

2:00:21.041 --> 2:00:22.974
and love them back.

2:00:23.112 --> 2:00:25.218
Because love is the one thing
in this world

2:00:25.356 --> 2:00:26.771
that's worth fighting for."

