2:01:47.507 --> 2:01:50.682
Dear Jordan,
when your father died,

2:01:50.820 --> 2:01:53.547
I thought my life was over.

2:01:53.685 --> 2:01:57.310
But the truth is,
it was just beginning.

2:01:59.208 --> 2:02:02.591
You and your dad both showed me
how beautiful life is

2:02:02.729 --> 2:02:06.940
when you live it below
your neck and in your heart.

2:02:07.078 --> 2:02:10.357
Risky place, the heart.

2:02:10.495 --> 2:02:13.326
Because it's fragile,
so it breaks.

2:02:13.464 --> 2:02:14.948
And it hurts.

2:02:16.846 --> 2:02:20.402
After your dad left, I tried
my best to feel nothing

2:02:20.540 --> 2:02:23.577
so my heart
would never break again.

2:02:23.715 --> 2:02:26.753
But even pain
is better than nothing.

2:02:26.891 --> 2:02:31.033
Because without pain,
it's impossible to find joy.

2:02:32.966 --> 2:02:35.244
I hope these words
will help you understand

2:02:35.382 --> 2:02:39.559
the remarkable love
your father and I shared.

2:02:39.697 --> 2:02:42.527
I want you to have
that kind of love, Jordan.

2:02:44.149 --> 2:02:46.013
The kind of love
that does not ask her

2:02:46.151 --> 2:02:49.051
to be anyone
other than who she is.

2:02:49.189 --> 2:02:51.364
And that does not ask
any more of you.

2:02:52.675 --> 2:02:54.608
T.J.:
Dear heavenly Father,

2:02:54.746 --> 2:02:56.576
thank you for bringing
us here as family

2:02:56.714 --> 2:02:58.060
to honor the life

2:02:58.198 --> 2:03:01.615
and remember the life
of Charles Monroe King.

2:03:03.686 --> 2:03:05.481
My prayer for you, Jordan,

2:03:05.619 --> 2:03:07.587
is that you carry with you
the knowledge

2:03:07.725 --> 2:03:11.487
that you will always have
two parents guiding you.

2:03:11.625 --> 2:03:13.765
But my mother's
intuition alone

2:03:13.903 --> 2:03:16.941
will not be enough
to teach you to be a man.

2:03:18.701 --> 2:03:23.326
For that, I give you
your father's journal.

2:03:23.465 --> 2:03:26.502
And the wisdom it contains.

2:03:26.640 --> 2:03:30.644
Its pages should give you
an idea of where you came from

2:03:30.782 --> 2:03:34.096
so you can decide
on exactly where you're going.

2:03:35.649 --> 2:03:37.824
I love you, son.

2:03:37.962 --> 2:03:41.690
Always and forever.

